<p>A custom sewing pattern generator is a tool that creates sewing patterns based on your individual body measurements rather than standard sizes. Instead of buying a pattern off the rack and altering it to fit, you enter your measurements, choose your garment and style preferences, and the generator drafts a pattern that is made for your body from the start.</p>
